      "examples": [
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0008",
          "cc_arg": 6,
          "speaker": "管家麥克",
          "text_id": 0,
          "text": "〔管家麥克〕\\n$n，很對不起，公爵有令，不許您進家門．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0024",
          "cc_arg": 19,
          "speaker": "$s公爵夫人",
          "text_id": 1,
          "text": "〔$s公爵夫人〕\\n哎呀，$n，這事已聽你父親說了，突然要你走出家，真殘酷呀！"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0048",
          "cc_arg": 19,
          "speaker": "$s公爵夫人",
          "text_id": 5,
          "text": "是啊，聽說跟馬丁內斯侯爵意見不和．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0063",
          "cc_arg": 19,
          "speaker": "$s公爵夫人",
          "text_id": 8,
          "text": "哎呀，洛克，你雖然長相平凡，但頭腦卻很不錯呀！"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0087",
          "cc_arg": 19,
          "speaker": "$s公爵夫人",
          "text_id": 12,
          "text": "好吧，我就把$n託給你了．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0090",
          "cc_arg": 19,
          "speaker": "$s公爵夫人",
          "text_id": 13,
          "text": "另外，$n，聽路琪亞小姐說你現在還沒有多少航海的資金，是麼？"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0099",
          "cc_arg": 19,
          "speaker": "$s公爵夫人",
          "text_id": 14,
          "text": "由於事情很突然，所以沒有準備好金幣，把這個給你吧．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x00a2",
          "cc_arg": 19,
          "speaker": "$s公爵夫人",
          "text_id": 15,
          "text": "這是以前我跟你父親要的銀髮飾．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x00ab",
          "cc_arg": 19,
          "speaker": "$s公爵夫人",
          "text_id": 16,
          "text": "把它賣掉當作資金吧，但對你爸要保密．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x00b4",
          "cc_arg": 19,
          "speaker": "$s公爵夫人",
          "text_id": 17,
          "text": "$n，一定要多加小心，上帝保佑你．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x00d0",
          "cc_arg": 6,
          "speaker": "管家麥克",
          "text_id": 18,
          "text": "〔管家麥克〕\\n$n，很對不起，公爵有令，不讓您進家門．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x00e0",
          "cc_arg": 6,
          "speaker": "管家麥克",
          "text_id": 19,
          "text": "〔管家麥克〕\\n$n，很對不起，公爵有令，不讓您進家門．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x00f2",
          "cc_arg": 6,
          "speaker": "管家麥克",
          "text_id": 21,
          "text": "大海像瞬間即改變其表情的怪物一樣危險．$n先生，請您一定要多加小心啊．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x010b",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 23,
          "text": "〔$s公爵〕\\n噢，是$n啊，你現在劍術練得如何了？"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x011d",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 25,
          "text": "是嗎，那麼航海術呢，學好啦？"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x012f",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 27,
          "text": "是嗎，那麼對地理學呢，擅長嗎？"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0141",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 29,
          "text": "$n，不要小看書本呀．書是先人的智慧，能把你從困境中救出來．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0153",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 31,
          "text": "$n，你彈琴怎麼樣？"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0165",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 33,
          "text": "是嗎？聽說你得到許多女孩子們的好感呀！"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0177",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 35,
          "text": "哈哈哈，有機會讓我聽聽吧！"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0180",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 36,
          "text": "$n！"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0192",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 38,
          "text": "今天有事告訴你．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01a4",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 40,
          "text": "你也知道吧，當我在你那個年齡時，已率領艦隊去討伐海盜了．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01b6",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 42,
          "text": "過去，不允許你從這個港口出航，是因為我擔心你不成熟，容易出事．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01bf",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 43,
          "text": "可是$s家族的人，不能老在陸地上待著．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01c8",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 44,
          "text": "你已經俱備了一定的知識，下一步是在海上實際鍛鍊．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01d1",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 45,
          "text": "這次派你去探險是葡萄牙首相兼海軍大臣萊昂·$s下達的命令．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01e3",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 47,
          "text": "去找出叫普萊斯特·約翰的國，也許你覺得這對你過於嚴厲．但是，除非你找到普萊斯特·約翰國，不然不許回家．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01ec",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 48,
          "text": "另外，我要發出公告，讓全城的人把你當作平民對待，你要有心理準備．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01f5",
          "cc_arg": 18,
          "speaker": "$s公爵",
          "text_id": 49,
          "text": "你的船已叫造船廠製造，在這期間作好出航前的準備吧．"
        }
      ]
    },
