      "examples": [
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x002d",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 2,
          "text": "請不要擔心，有那麼一天找到普萊斯特·約翰國後，一定回來的．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0036",
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 3,
          "text": "太太，這是$s家人的呀！"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x003f",
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 4,
          "text": "可是，船長，我聽說公爵是跟某個貴族之間有恩怨呀．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0051",
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 6,
          "text": "問題就在這裡，由於他的原因，公爵無法離開這個國家．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x005a",
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 7,
          "text": "所以，很可能想要一個能替代他的優秀的人才．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x006c",
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 9,
          "text": "當然，因為長期跟隨過公爵嘛．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0075",
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 10,
          "text": "噢，不管怎麼說，我對少爺出海是贊成的．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x007e",
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 11,
          "text": "因為沒有比航海更能鍛練男子漢的．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x00e9",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 20,
          "text": "知道了，我只是想跟你告別呀．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0102",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 22,
          "text": "聽說父親叫我．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0114",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 24,
          "text": "還行，當然只是跟以前比較說的，若和父親比試的話，只能五場贏一場吧．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0126",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 26,
          "text": "大致從理論上學了一些，但沒有實際經驗，只是紙上談兵呀！"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0138",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 28,
          "text": "這個事嗎，由於不允許我離開里斯本，只能從書本上學了一些．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x014a",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 30,
          "text": "是．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x015c",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 32,
          "text": "那是個人的愛好，沒法在人家的面前彈奏．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x016e",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 34,
          "text": "請不要笑話我．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0189",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 37,
          "text": "是．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x019b",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 39,
          "text": "是什麼事啊？"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01ad",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 41,
          "text": "是，我明白．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x01da",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 46,
          "text": "是．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x020a",
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 51,
          "text": "〔老水手洛克〕\\n我在這裡．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x021c",
          "cc_arg": 31,
          "speaker": "老水手洛克",
          "text_id": 53,
          "text": "知道了，船長，啊！不對，公爵閣下．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x0268",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 59,
          "text": "哈哈哈，是路琪亞要我彈，我怎能不彈呀．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x027d",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 61,
          "text": "是嘛，那我早點回去了．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x02c7",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 66,
          "text": "是啊，這是$s家的啊．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x02d0",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 67,
          "text": "但不知資金辦得怎麼樣了．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x030f",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 74,
          "text": "不，這錢我不能收．我沒辦法還您呀．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x032a",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 77,
          "text": "是父親嗎？"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x034b",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 80,
          "text": "那辦不到，我已經不能再進家門了．"
        },
        {
          "script": "Snr1.chunk0.sub0",
          "offset_hex": "0x035d",
          "cc_arg": 0,
          "speaker": null,
          "text_id": 82,
          "text": "喂，路琪亞！"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
